Package nl.naturalis.nda.elasticsearch.load.crs

Package that handles the import of the CRS data sources.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CrsExtractor
    The extraction component for the CRS import.
    CrsFindInSource
    Utility class for searching the locally stored XML files for a value.
    CrsHarvester
    Harvests the CRS OAI service and saves its output to files on the local file system.
    CrsImportAll
    Class that manages the import of CRS specimens and multimedia.
    CrsImportUtil
    Class providing common functionality for CRS imports.
    CrsMultiMediaImport
    Class that manages the import of CRS multimedia.
    CrsMultiMediaImportOffline
    Class that manages the import of CRS multimedia.
    CrsMultiMediaLoader
    The loader component for the CRS multimedia import.
    CrsMultiMediaTransformer
    The transformer component for the CRS multimedia import.
    CrsSpecimenImport
    Class that manages the import of CRS specimens.
    CrsSpecimenImportOffline
    Class that manages the import of CRS specimens.
    CrsSpecimenLoader
    The transformer component for the CRS specimen import.
    CrsSpecimenTransformer
    The transformation component for the CRS specimen import.
